# Lab Setup Instructions

This document contains all steps I followed to create this AWS lab.

## VPC Setup

1. Created a VPC with CIDR `10.0.0.0/16`
2. Created a public subnet with `10.0.1.0/24`
3. Attached an Internet Gateway (IGW)
4. Updated route table: added `0.0.0.0/0` â†’ IGW

## EC2 Setup

1. Launched Amazon Linux 2 EC2 in public subnet
2. Enabled auto-assign public IP
3. Created key pair and downloaded `.pem` file
4. Allowed SSH (port 22) from my IP in Security Group

## SSH Access

Used Git Bash:
```bash
chmod 400 my-key.pem
ssh -i my-key.pem ec2-user@<EC2_Public_IP>
